Image Options
Here you can give your logo a title.
Title

Here you can customize your x-axis's label. The default is "Position".
X-Axis Label

Here you can customize your y-axis's label. The default is "Position".
Y-Axis Label

Choose color scheme - the default colors are orange (G), red (T/U), blue (C) and green (A) for nucleic acids
and green (G,S,T,Y,C,Q,N), blue (K,R,H), red (D,E) and black (A,V,L,I,P,W,F,M) for amino acids. Choose Black&White option to color all symbols black.
